{"tid":110861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國獲邀出席「反對器官販賣全球峰會」","createTime":"2017-02-07T04:18:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T05:13:15.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae4777dc8d2692baa02b964b311b493efb807f24","tid":110861,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T04:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170207/_2017020710265995185.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170207%2F_2017020710265995185.jpg&h=6d4edc34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梵蒂岡一連兩日舉行「反對器官販賣全球峰會」，中國前衛生部副部長、現任人體器官捐獻與移植委員會主席黃潔夫，率領高層代表團出席，是中國第一次獲邀出席由國際權威組織舉辦的器官移植領域峰會。<br />\n<br />\n傳媒報道，他將向世界各國分享器官捐獻與移植管理的中國方案。<br />\n<br />\n但英國傳媒報道，中國參加今次會議，引起一些人不滿，梵蒂岡則為邀請中國出席辯護，強調峰會目的是學術探討，並非「重複有爭議的政治主張」。<br />\n<br />\n分析認為，梵蒂岡正積極改善與中國的關係。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/332801-國際-中國獲邀出席「反對器官販賣全球峰會」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F332801-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%8D%B2%E9%82%80%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E3%80%8C%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E5%99%A8%E5%AE%98%E8%B2%A9%E8%B3%A3%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%B3%B0%E6%9C%83%E3%80%8D&d=BdEUjZUsFG%2BHnlCy9NhCd7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=b0cec1ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F332801-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%8D%B2%E9%82%80%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E3%80%8C%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E5%99%A8%E5%AE%98%E8%B2%A9%E8%B3%A3%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%B3%B0%E6%9C%83%E3%80%8D&h=0a360547\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/332801-國際-中國獲邀出席「反對器官販賣全球峰會」</a>"},{"pid":"ea4ca11a711ca28f4bf5d2541a834d084feea035","tid":110861,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T04:22:31.000Z","msg":"人不要面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4faab37d907c1c9bf673d401304f117b591023","tid":110861,"uid":77158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T04:30:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e618a704f0fa3406f4639d8da308bd26d96b09eb","tid":110861,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T05:13:15.000Z","msg":"最後一位教宗 係敵基督 中曬"}]}